# Vite frontend env: these values are injected at build time.
# Copy to frontend/.env.local or set them in your static host build environment.
# Do not leave required chain IDs empty and do not replace them with 0x0.
# If any required VITE_* ID is missing or invalid, `pnpm -C frontend build` fails fast.

